--- !u!114 &235320793
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 235320792}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 3961fb74196f2a44a837ac22e48280d4, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  avatarSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 8ef80ca11fe0be54bb14d1e0a5d3a35d, type: 3}
  promptText: Press Enter to Talk
  textHeight: 0.5
  fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 358d097249919594790a24b77037a3b0, type: 2}
  canGiveSkillPoints: 1
  triggersSceneTransition: 0
  nextSceneName: 
  transitionDelay: 0.5
  bounceAmplitude: 0.02
  bounceSpeed: 3
  dialogueLines:
  - "Stop. Don\u2019t move."
  - "Your readings are unstable \u2014 two bodies, one core, constantly correcting
    itself."
  - "That kind of split shouldn\u2019t be survivable\u2026 yet here you are."
  - One form vents astral energy. The other rips through space to stay ahead of collapse.
  - Planet Echo is getting worse.
  - The terrain ahead is fractured, hostile, and crawling with corrupted constructs.
  - "If you keep fighting at your current limits, you won\u2019t make it far."
  - "Your power isn\u2019t gone."
  - "It\u2019s deliberately restricted \u2014 a containment response."
  - I can override part of it.
  - Two control nodes. No more. (Press T to access skill tree)
  - Use them to reinforce what you rely on most.
  - "More output from astral fire\u2026 or tighter control over movement."
  - Choose wrong, and the next zone will punish you for it.
  - "That\u2019s all the help you\u2019re getting."
  - "Move carefully. Things ahead don\u2019t miss twice."
  npcAudioClips:
  - {fileID: 8300000, guid: 0290c3b02010d2c41b5cd78237694033, type: 3}
